# ==== Cowork / Claude local config ====
# Ignore everything inside .claude EXCEPT the project docs we want versioned.
# CLAUDE.md is the entry point Claude Code reads on every prompt.
# PROJECT.md is the human-friendly full-context doc (see .claude/PROJECT.md).
.claude/*
!.claude/CLAUDE.md
!.claude/PROJECT.md
install-skills.ps1
link-skills.ps1
